      <title>壳牌维持回购，削减债务，利润超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/shell-maintains-buyback-reduces-debt-as-profit-beats-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌公司公布第二季度收益超过预期，并确认再回购 35 亿美元股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/shell-maintains-buyback-reduces-debt-as-profit-beats-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ninewide 称英国房价连续第三个月上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/uk-house-prices-rise-for-third-month-in-july-nationwide-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家顶级抵押贷款机构表示，英国房价连续第三个月上涨，进一步证明市场在 16 年来最高的借贷成本面前正在趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/uk-house-prices-rise-for-third-month-in-july-nationwide-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:03:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宝马盈利因中国主要市场需求疲软而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bmw-earnings-drop-on-waning-demand-in-key-china-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马汽车公司 (BMW AG) 第二季度盈利出现下滑，原因是其主要市场中国销量下滑，这家德国公司加入了越来越多面临需求放缓困境的汽车制造商的行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bmw-earnings-drop-on-waning-demand-in-key-china-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国农业信贷银行盈利超预期，瞄准顶级 FICC 角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/credit-agricole-beats-estimates-as-investment-bank-outperforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole SA) 公布的第二季度利润超过分析师预期，原因是交易员和交易员表现出色，且该银行开始看到法国加息带来的延迟效益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/credit-agricole-beats-estimates-as-investment-bank-outperforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 04:53:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元贬值致日本出口商股价创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/japan-s-stocks-tumble-most-since-march-as-exporters-falls-on-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市下跌，东证指数在全线抛售中创下2020年4月以来的最大跌幅，因为日元大幅上涨给出口商带来压力，而央行加息拖累了房地产股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/japan-s-stocks-tumble-most-since-march-as-exporters-falls-on-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:32:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
